node.text:
Our Vegan Curry plate, with Rice & Peas and Channa(chickpeas). üçõ

As a business, dealing with the effects of the coronavirus on the world, we have had to adjust to the daily, ever-evolving restrictions and shutdowns. Over the years, we have been happy and grateful to meet and serve you all, our customers, and are extremely thankful for your continued support and kindness towards us. 
As of today, despite the fact that some of the farmers markets in Los Angeles have reopened under the advisement of Mayor Garcetti, all food vendors have been told that we cannot continue to sell at the markets. For now, only farmers, selling vegetables and fruit are allowed. 
We will continue to keep you all updated and when the farmers markets will be returning to normal operations. We miss not being at Baldwin Hills Crenshaw FM and Atwater Village FM. ‚ú®For the time being, we are continuing to do deliveries of our prepackaged meals and pastries. We are here to serve you as best we can. Deliveries will be made on Saturdays and Sundays, through preorders. Contact us through DM, phone, or text.‚ú® Stay safe, healthy, and well. Thank you for always supporting our business, it means the world to us!

In gratitude,
